<ul><li> Early on in ClockUp's <em>Euphoria</em>, Rika does the skirt-grab variant of this trope while being trapped with the others.
</li><li> In <em> Lovely Day of Girlfriends &amp; Me</em>, Yuka does the skirt-grab variant of this while on a date with Shou, before finally <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/PottyFailure" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/PottyFailure">just going on the ground.</a>
</li></ul></div>
